<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .intimation {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      color: white;
      padding-left: 140px;
      padding-right: 140px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18px;
    }

    .message {
      padding-left: 76px;
      padding-right: 71px;
      text-align: left;
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18px;
    }

    .button {
      width: 180px;
      height: 30px;
      background-color: rgba(253, 147, 32, 0.8);
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: white;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {

      .intimation,
      .message {
        padding-left: 12%;
        padding-right: 12%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div
    style="width:100%;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;background: #033348;padding:2% 4%;padding-bottom: 4%;">
    <img style="height: 60px;width: 60px;padding-left:4%;margin-top:1%;margin-bottom:1.5%;"
      src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/mittarv_logo_white_tm.png" />

    <div style="background: #054A68;padding:2% 4%;margin-bottom:2%;border-radius: 5px;text-align: center;">
      <img style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:1.5%; width: 98px; height: 43px;"
        src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/welcome.png" />
      <h2
        style="margin-bottom: 30px;color:white;font-weight:700;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5%; text-align: center;">
        User Status Inquiry</h2>
      <h2
        style="margin-bottom: 25px;color:white;font-weight:700;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5%; text-align: center;">
        Dear {{TCname}},</h2>
      <p class="message">
        We are reaching out to you because you were identified as a trusted contact for {{username}}, who is a user of
        our app. We have not heard from them in some time, and we are concerned about their well-being. As part of our
        commitment to ensuring the safety and security of our users, we are reaching out to our users' trusted contacts
        to inquire about their status.<br><br>

        We Request you fill out the Inform Status Change form on Mitt Arv App. On the Homepage, go to People who trust
        me -> Select the User's Name -> Inform Status Change -> Select the updated status -> Confirm.<br><br>

        {{#if isSingleTC}}
        However, if you don't fill out the form within the next 10 days, we will deliver the user's data to the
        recipients added. We understand that this may be a sensitive topic, and we want to assure you that we are taking
        this inquiry seriously. Your assistance in this matter is greatly appreciated, and we thank you in advance for
        your cooperation.<br><br>
        {{else}}
        We understand that this may be a sensitive topic, and we want to assure you that we are taking this inquiry
        seriously. Your assistance in this matter is greatly appreciated, and we thank you in advance for your
        cooperation. If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out to us directly. We are
        committed to maintaining the privacy and security of our users, and we will handle this inquiry with the utmost
        care and respect.<br><br>
        {{/if}}

        If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out to us directly. We are committed to
        maintaining the privacy and security of our users, and we will handle this inquiry with the utmost care and
        respect.<br><br>

        Thank you for your attention to this matter.
      </p>
      <button class="button">
        <a href="{{redirectUrl}}" target="_blank"
          style="color:white;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;letter-spacing: 1.5%;margin: auto; text-decoration:none">
          Inform Status Change
        </a>
      </button>
      <div class="intimation">
      </div>
      <p
        style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;color:white;font-weight:400;letter-spacing: 1.5%;text-align: center;">
        Best,<br>Team<span
          style=" font-size: 12px;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #84B5D2;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 1.5%;">
          Mitt
          Arv</span><br>
        <b>Zero - Life - Infinity</b>
      </p>
      <hr
        style="height:2px;border-width:0;color:#033348;background-color:#033348;margin-top:2.5%;margin-bottom:2.5%;width:110%;margin-left: -5%;">
      <p
        style="text-align: center;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-size: 12px;color: white;letter-spacing: 1.5%;">
        For any inquiries, kindly reach out to us at : support@mittarv.com
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>